title: Pattiyal
subTitle: Two best friends Kosi and Selvam are contract killers who are given targets by Sami. They fall in love, but their profession becomes a hurdle and the two cannot lead normal lives.

title: Kovil Yanai
subTitle: Deeply in love, Raja and Kaveri face numerous challenges. However, with the help of a temple elephant, they conquer all adversities and secure their happiness.

title: Putham Pudhu Payanam
subTitle: Vivek, Narayanan, Kannan and Babu, terminal patients, escape from the a hospital and reach a village. There, they aid Nirmala and Kumar's union by eliminating Sivalingam, who opposes their relationship.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: Sonnalthan Kaadhala
subTitle: Roja, a part-time singer, works at a finance company where her colleague, Murali, is madly in love with her. However, Roja rejects his proposal as she is the sole breadwinner of her large family.

title: Aduthathu Albert
subTitle: Although Albert, a Christian boy, and Radha, a Brahmin girl, hate each other, they decide to help their respective sister and brother who are in love.

title: Santhitha Velai
subTitle: During a trip, Aadalarasu meets his ailing doppelganger, Thirunaavukkarasu, who puts forth a request. After the latter's death, Aadalarasu sets out to fulfil the promise he made to his lookalike.

title: Naan Sivappu Manithan
subTitle: A Tamil professor and his friend try to stop the prostitution and illicit liquor trade in their neighbourhood. However, due to their work, a criminal gang begins to attack their families.

title: Vennila Kabadi Kuzhu
subTitle: Having never won a tournament, a team of kabaddi players are ridiculed by their villagers. Their redemption finally arrives while playing in Madurai, for which they pay a heavy price.

title: Ambigai Neril Vanthaal
subTitle: After a lot of persuasion, Devaki agrees to marry Ravi. However, the marriage becomes a bitter struggle for her when she comes to know that Ravi is a drunkard and a womaniser.

title: Ambigai Neril Vanthaal
subTitle: After a lot of persuasion, Devaki agrees to marry Ravi. However, the marriage becomes a bitter struggle for her when she comes to know that Ravi is a drunkard and a womaniser.

title: Aarohanam
subTitle: Nirmala, a middle-aged woman, who has bipolar disorder, goes missing just a few days before her daughter's marriage. Thereafter, her worried children set out to look for her.

title: Vettri Kani
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: Bose
subTitle: When the man who hired him turns out to be a criminal, Bose loses his temper and shoots him. However, this action bears heavy consequences on his personal life.

title: Ethir Kaatru
subTitle: A dubious financial company uses an unemployed youth as a scapegoat to conceal their fraudulent business. However, his suspicious death compels a journalist to expose the firm's deceptive practices.

title: Makkal Veeran
subTitle: A camerawoman helps a fiery mechanic become a journalist. However, when an evil politician commits a crime, the journalist decides to destroy his political career.

title: Paayum Puli
subTitle: A man with mental challenges decides to join a martial arts school in order to hone his fighting skills and avenge the murder of his sister.

title: Naaigal Jaakirathai
subTitle: A police officer enlists the help of a trained military dog in order to locate the whereabouts of his wife, who is kidnapped.

title: Thambikku Intha Ooru
subTitle: Akil, a restaurateur from Singapore, is taken aback after learning that he has been adopted and sets out on a journey to Chengalpet in order to find his biological parents.

title: Thambikku Intha Ooru
subTitle: Akil, a restaurateur from Singapore, is taken aback after learning that he has been adopted and sets out on a journey to Chengalpet in order to find his biological parents.

title: Aadu Puli Attam
subTitle: Mandhiran is a gangster who kills innocent people for money. When he meets Gayathri he falls in love with her and tries to woo her by helping her family.

title: Selva Magan
subTitle: The sudden death of a rich woman's son paves way for her relatives to exploit her. However, when a young man enters her life, she finds a ray of hope as he vows to protect her.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Vaitheeswaran
subTitle: After the death of Saravanan, a sage tells his mother that her son will reincarnate if she never leaves the temple and prays. Thirty years later, an agnostic Dr Bala meets the mother to treat her.

title: Gopala Gopala
subTitle: Gopal causes much angst among his male neighbours as he is friendly with their spouses. They are relieved when he marries Usha. But Usha leaves him after learning that he was married once before.

title: Marupadiyum
subTitle: Married to Murali, a film director, Thulasi is shocked to discover her husband having an affair with his heroin. She finds a new meaning to life after divorcing him, but Murali's life turns otherwise.

title: Murattu Kaalai
subTitle: Kaalaiyan is a landlord who lives a humble life with his brothers despite his wealth. However, a greedy man from a neighbouring village plots to take over his land.

title: Ramanaa
subTitle: Ramanaa, a professor, heads a secret group that eliminates corruption from society. They kidnap 15 most corrupt employees from each government department and kill the most unscrupulous one.

title: Amarkalam
subTitle: Vasu, an unruly man, fights with Mohana, the daughter of a police officer, over a movie reel. Thereafter, the two fall in love but face unforeseen problems while they try to unite.
